query: SELECT p.*, s.name as service_name, s.id as service_id, c.name as country_name, c.id as country_id FROM prices p JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id WHERE s.smshubCode = 'wa' AND c.code = 'brazil'
